{
  "video_id": "sdF5OXT6Bxw",
  "title": "Model 5, V5 - Subsequent Events EXPLAINED with Examples",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 2990.0,
      "end_time": 5540.0,
      "text": "Hi, Else here, and today we&#39;ll be talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5540.0,
      "end_time": 7370.0,
      "text": "about subsequent events."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7370.0,
      "end_time": 10040.0,
      "text": "What is a subsequent event?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10040.0,
      "end_time": 12260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an event that occurs between a business&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12260.0,
      "end_time": 14930.0,
      "text": "year-end date and the date that the financial statements are"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14930.0,
      "end_time": 16910.0,
      "text": "approved for issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16910.0,
      "end_time": 19040.0,
      "text": "What does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 19040.0,
      "end_time": 21370.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at a timeline to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21370.0,
      "end_time": 25030.0,
      "text": "A fiscal year has a start date and a year-end date."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25030.0,
      "end_time": 28910.0,
      "text": "The fiscal year lasts either one year or an operating cycle"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28910.0,
      "end_time": 31120.0,
      "text": "whichever is longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31120.0,
      "end_time": 35800.0,
      "text": "I made this fiscal year one year ending December 31st."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35800.0,
      "end_time": 39160.0,
      "text": "Note that 2/3 of all companies have a year-end date that&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39160.0,
      "end_time": 41470.0,
      "text": "December 31st or close to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41470.0,
      "end_time": 43270.0,
      "text": "So it makes sense that you frequently"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43270.0,
      "end_time": 47510.0,
      "text": "see this date as a year-end date for companies in textbooks."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 47510.0,
      "end_time": 49940.0,
      "text": "Between the start and end dates of the fiscal year"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49940.0,
      "end_time": 51980.0,
      "text": "is the reporting period."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51980.0,
      "end_time": 54410.0,
      "text": "All transactions that take place during this period"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54410.0,
      "end_time": 57121.0,
      "text": "must be reported in the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57121.0,
      "end_time": 59120.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the basis of accrual accounting, which is"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59120.0,
      "end_time": 62200.0,
      "text": "required under IFRS and ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 62200.0,
      "end_time": 64330.0,
      "text": "The year-end date is the cut off point"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64330.0,
      "end_time": 68170.0,
      "text": "for recognizing transactions in that fiscal period."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68170.0,
      "end_time": 70660.0,
      "text": "The cut off date is the point when one reporting period"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70660.0,
      "end_time": 72970.0,
      "text": "ends and the next one starts."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72970.0,
      "end_time": 76120.0,
      "text": "However, after the year-end, several weeks or months"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76120.0,
      "end_time": 78160.0,
      "text": "may pass before the board of directors"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78160.0,
      "end_time": 81130.0,
      "text": "approves the financial statements for issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81130.0,
      "end_time": 82720.0,
      "text": "During that time the business will"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 82720.0,
      "end_time": 85740.0,
      "text": "do things like count and price inventory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85740.0,
      "end_time": 87880.0,
      "text": "prepare adjusting entries, ensure"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 87880.0,
      "end_time": 89770.0,
      "text": "the accounting records are complete,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89770.0,
      "end_time": 92830.0,
      "text": "and have the financial statements audited."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 92830.0,
      "end_time": 94720.0,
      "text": "This period between the cut off date"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 94720.0,
      "end_time": 97120.0,
      "text": "and the date when the financial statements are approved"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 97120.0,
      "end_time": 100150.0,
      "text": "is called the subsequent events period."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100150.0,
      "end_time": 103210.0,
      "text": "During this period, events that impact the company&#39;s business"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 103210.0,
      "end_time": 106600.0,
      "text": "in a significant way may occur."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106600.0,
      "end_time": 108820.0,
      "text": "If material, should these events be"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 108820.0,
      "end_time": 110920.0,
      "text": "reflected in the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110920.0,
      "end_time": 114890.0,
      "text": "even though they happened after the cut off date?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 114890.0,
      "end_time": 117380.0,
      "text": "The simple answer is yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117380.0,
      "end_time": 119660.0,
      "text": "If the events are material, the stakeholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119660.0,
      "end_time": 122450.0,
      "text": "would need this information to help them predict the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 122450.0,
      "end_time": 124160.0,
      "text": "and make decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124160.0,
      "end_time": 126380.0,
      "text": "Without this information, the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126380.0,
      "end_time": 128120.0,
      "text": "may be misleading."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128120.0,
      "end_time": 131390.0,
      "text": "However, the answer is far more complicated than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131390.0,
      "end_time": 136220.0,
      "text": "It actually depends on what the event is and when it happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136220.0,
      "end_time": 139530.0,
      "text": "Subsequent events are divided into two types--"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139530.0,
      "end_time": 142920.0,
      "text": "adjusting events and non-adjusting events."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 142920.0,
      "end_time": 145560.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s cover each individually."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 145560.0,
      "end_time": 147330.0,
      "text": "Events in the subsequent event period"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 147330.0,
      "end_time": 151620.0,
      "text": "are adjusting events if the actual condition existed"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151620.0,
      "end_time": 156000.0,
      "text": "before the cut off date but in the subsequent period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 156000.0,
      "end_time": 158100.0,
      "text": "additional evidence comes to light"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 158100.0,
      "end_time": 161100.0,
      "text": "that allows the company to improve the measurement"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 161100.0,
      "end_time": 163320.0,
      "text": "of a previous estimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 163320.0,
      "end_time": 165150.0,
      "text": "This includes information that would"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165150.0,
      "end_time": 167040.0,
      "text": "have been recorded in the accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 167040.0,
      "end_time": 169900.0,
      "text": "if it had been known at the cut off date."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 169900.0,
      "end_time": 172680.0,
      "text": "This means that with regards to measurement"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 172680.0,
      "end_time": 175840.0,
      "text": "the preparer should use the best information available,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 175840.0,
      "end_time": 178830.0,
      "text": "including information available during the subsequent events"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178830.0,
      "end_time": 183870.0,
      "text": "period as long as the condition existed during the reporting"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 183870.0,
      "end_time": 184800.0,
      "text": "period."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 184800.0,
      "end_time": 186780.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s critical."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 186780.0,
      "end_time": 189240.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s clarify this concept with a few examples using"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 189240.0,
      "end_time": 190910.0,
      "text": "the timeline."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190910.0,
      "end_time": 194120.0,
      "text": "Assume there is a major technological change"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 194120.0,
      "end_time": 197300.0,
      "text": "and you find out about it during the subsequent event period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 197300.0,
      "end_time": 199770.0,
      "text": "say February 12th."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 199770.0,
      "end_time": 202860.0,
      "text": "This change will make your inventory worth far less,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 202860.0,
      "end_time": 206287.0,
      "text": "because few customers will want to buy it anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 206287.0,
      "end_time": 208620.0,
      "text": "You found out about that change in the subsequent events"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 208620.0,
      "end_time": 209130.0,
      "text": "period."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 209130.0,
      "end_time": 212220.0,
      "text": "But what if that technological change actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 212220.0,
      "end_time": 214830.0,
      "text": "occurred on November 21st?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 214830.0,
      "end_time": 218220.0,
      "text": "Note that the condition, the technological change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 218220.0,
      "end_time": 220830.0,
      "text": "existed before the cut off date."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 220830.0,
      "end_time": 222540.0,
      "text": "Even though the evidence of the change"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 222540.0,
      "end_time": 225180.0,
      "text": "was found during the subsequent events period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 225180.0,
      "end_time": 227940.0,
      "text": "the measurement of the inventory owned at year-end"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 227940.0,
      "end_time": 230790.0,
      "text": "must be adjusted, written down, to the lower of cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 230790.0,
      "end_time": 232990.0,
      "text": "or net realizable value."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 232990.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "This meets the requirements of an adjusting event, which"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 238720.0,
      "text": "means that the adjusting entry must be recorded"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 238720.0,
      "end_time": 240220.0,
      "text": "in the accounting system."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 240220.0,
      "end_time": 242680.0,
      "text": "And the updated value of inventory"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 242680.0,
      "end_time": 245620.0,
      "text": "must be reported on the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 245620.0,
      "end_time": 248080.0,
      "text": "even though the evidence was discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 248080.0,
      "end_time": 251030.0,
      "text": "during the subsequent events period."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 251030.0,
      "end_time": 252950.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do another example."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 252950.0,
      "end_time": 255680.0,
      "text": "Say that a customer declares bankruptcy on March 12th"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 255680.0,
      "end_time": 258649.0,
      "text": "before the financial statements are approved for issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 258649.0,
      "end_time": 260750.0,
      "text": "Would this fact be reflected in the year"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 260750.0,
      "end_time": 263870.0,
      "text": "in financial statements by adjusting the accounts?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 263870.0,
      "end_time": 265700.0,
      "text": "The answer is yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 265700.0,
      "end_time": 268250.0,
      "text": "The financial statements would be adjusted."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 268250.0,
      "end_time": 270320.0,
      "text": "For estimates, such as the allowance for doubtful"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 270320.0,
      "end_time": 273440.0,
      "text": "accounts, information during the subsequent events period"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 273440.0,
      "end_time": 275960.0,
      "text": "is used to determine the allowance including"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 275960.0,
      "end_time": 278480.0,
      "text": "actual collections and defaults."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 278480.0,
      "end_time": 279960.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 279960.0,
      "end_time": 282390.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s likely the customer was already"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 282390.0,
      "end_time": 285600.0,
      "text": "in financial difficulty before the cut off date."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 285600.0,
      "end_time": 288770.0,
      "text": "We can adjust the measurement of the AFDA."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 288770.0,
      "end_time": 291380.0,
      "text": "This is also true for accounts, such as sales returns"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 291380.0,
      "end_time": 295750.0,
      "text": "and allowances, which are often estimated at period end."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 295750.0,
      "end_time": 298090.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do one more example."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 298090.0,
      "end_time": 300850.0,
      "text": "Say that a lawsuit was settled during the subsequent events"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 300850.0,
      "end_time": 301750.0,
      "text": "period."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 301750.0,
      "end_time": 304240.0,
      "text": "On January 31st, was your company"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 304240.0,
      "end_time": 307590.0,
      "text": "on the hook for $2 million of damages?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 307590.0,
      "end_time": 310290.0,
      "text": "If the event that caused the lawsuit happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 310290.0,
      "end_time": 313350.0,
      "text": "within the reporting period, say in June of the reporting"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 313350.0,
      "end_time": 316200.0,
      "text": "period, then the settlement of the lawsuit"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 316200.0,
      "end_time": 318930.0,
      "text": "must be reported in the year-end financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 318930.0,
      "end_time": 321660.0,
      "text": "by recording a loss on the income statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 321660.0,
      "end_time": 324760.0,
      "text": "and a liability on the balance sheet."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 324760.0,
      "end_time": 327280.0,
      "text": "This is, again, because the condition existed"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 327280.0,
      "end_time": 328840.0,
      "text": "before the year-end date."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 328840.0,
      "end_time": 331180.0,
      "text": "The evidence, in the form of the settlement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 331180.0,
      "end_time": 333640.0,
      "text": "was available in the subsequent events period."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 333640.0,
      "end_time": 336490.0,
      "text": "And that affects the way you would measure the impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 336490.0,
      "end_time": 339930.0,
      "text": "of the lawsuit on the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 339930.0,
      "end_time": 343240.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s now turn our attention to non-adjusting events."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 343240.0,
      "end_time": 345390.0,
      "text": "These are events where the condition did not"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 345390.0,
      "end_time": 347340.0,
      "text": "exist before the cut off date."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 347340.0,
      "end_time": 349940.0,
      "text": "An example would be an accident that destroys"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 349940.0,
      "end_time": 352620.0,
      "text": "a factory on January 28th."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 352620.0,
      "end_time": 355095.0,
      "text": "Although the factory definitely existed before the cut"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 355095.0,
      "end_time": 358515.0,
      "text": "off date, the destruction did not happen before the cut"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 358515.0,
      "end_time": 359930.0,
      "text": "off date."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 359930.0,
      "end_time": 361650.0,
      "text": "The evidence is, again, available in"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 361650.0,
      "end_time": 363150.0,
      "text": "the subsequent events period."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 363150.0,
      "end_time": 366770.0,
      "text": "But this new evidence would never affect the amounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 366770.0,
      "end_time": 368370.0,
      "text": "on the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 368370.0,
      "end_time": 371700.0,
      "text": "There would be no adjustment to the account balances."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 371700.0,
      "end_time": 373790.0,
      "text": "Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 373790.0,
      "end_time": 375830.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at an example using the timeline"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 375830.0,
      "end_time": 379570.0,
      "text": "to see why there are no adjustments necessary."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 379570.0,
      "end_time": 382540.0,
      "text": "Say that on February 9th there is a severe decline"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 382540.0,
      "end_time": 383770.0,
      "text": "in financial markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 383770.0,
      "end_time": 386020.0,
      "text": "And suddenly, the investment your company"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 386020.0,
      "end_time": 389410.0,
      "text": "made in the shares of Apple Inc take a dive."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 389410.0,
      "end_time": 392860.0,
      "text": "Your investment, a long-term asset on your balance sheet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 392860.0,
      "end_time": 396370.0,
      "text": "is now worth half of what it was at year-end."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 396370.0,
      "end_time": 398200.0,
      "text": "Should the value of your investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 398200.0,
      "end_time": 401920.0,
      "text": "be adjusted on the December 31st financial statements?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 401920.0,
      "end_time": 406190.0,
      "text": "The answer is absolutely not."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 406190.0,
      "end_time": 407590.0,
      "text": "Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 407590.0,
      "end_time": 410605.0,
      "text": "Because the condition of the market changed after the cut"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 410605.0,
      "end_time": 412910.0,
      "text": "off date not before."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 412910.0,
      "end_time": 414640.0,
      "text": "Even though the evidence, which would"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 414640.0,
      "end_time": 416710.0,
      "text": "be the decline in the market, happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 416710.0,
      "end_time": 418630.0,
      "text": "in the subsequent events period, it"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 418630.0,
      "end_time": 420850.0,
      "text": "would never impact the measuring of the accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 420850.0,
      "end_time": 423130.0,
      "text": "on the financial statements at year-end."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 423130.0,
      "end_time": 424420.0,
      "text": "Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 424420.0,
      "end_time": 429220.0,
      "text": "Because the condition did not exist before the cut off date."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 429220.0,
      "end_time": 431440.0,
      "text": "Other examples of non-adjusting events"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 431440.0,
      "end_time": 435870.0,
      "text": "would be the loss of assets due to fire, flood, hurricane, et"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 435870.0,
      "end_time": 439540.0,
      "text": "cetera; a lawsuit where the event, such as the patent"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 439540.0,
      "end_time": 441655.0,
      "text": "infringement, happened after the cut"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 441655.0,
      "end_time": 444550.0,
      "text": "off date in the subsequent period;"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 444550.0,
      "end_time": 446890.0,
      "text": "or the sale of a company shares, the purchase"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 446890.0,
      "end_time": 451280.0,
      "text": "of another company, the issue of new debt, the list goes on."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 451280.0,
      "end_time": 455560.0,
      "text": "So can we totally ignore all non-adjusting events?"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 455560.0,
      "end_time": 457810.0,
      "text": "Absolutely not."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 457810.0,
      "end_time": 461230.0,
      "text": "If the event materially affects the assets, liabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 461230.0,
      "end_time": 463360.0,
      "text": "or future operations of the business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 463360.0,
      "end_time": 465130.0,
      "text": "it must be disclosed in the notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 465130.0,
      "end_time": 467860.0,
      "text": "to the financial statements at a minimum."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 467860.0,
      "end_time": 470620.0,
      "text": "It may also result in supplemental schedules."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 470620.0,
      "end_time": 473710.0,
      "text": "Or if very material, it may require"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 473710.0,
      "end_time": 476270.0,
      "text": "supplemental financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 476270.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "These would be prepared to show what the financial position"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 482500.0,
      "text": "would be if the event had occurred before the balance"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 482500.0,
      "end_time": 483850.0,
      "text": "sheet date--"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 483850.0,
      "end_time": 487360.0,
      "text": "anything necessary to ensure that stakeholders clearly"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 487360.0,
      "end_time": 489910.0,
      "text": "understand the impact of the subsequent events"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 489910.0,
      "end_time": 492820.0,
      "text": "on the business&#39;s financial position or profitability"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 492820.0,
      "end_time": 494320.0,
      "text": "in the future--"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 494320.0,
      "end_time": 496450.0,
      "text": "this is required to ensure the company is"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 496450.0,
      "end_time": 499240.0,
      "text": "following full disclosure."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 499240.0,
      "end_time": 502210.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s just summarize everything we&#39;ve learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 502210.0,
      "end_time": 504760.0,
      "text": "In both adjusting and non-adjusting events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 504760.0,
      "end_time": 507730.0,
      "text": "the evidence is always available in the subsequent events"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 507730.0,
      "end_time": 508270.0,
      "text": "period."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 508270.0,
      "end_time": 511810.0,
      "text": "But for adjusting events, the condition"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 511810.0,
      "end_time": 515470.0,
      "text": "existed before the cut off date in the reporting period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 515470.0,
      "end_time": 518020.0,
      "text": "which is why the event affects the measurement"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 518020.0,
      "end_time": 521140.0,
      "text": "of the estimates and is recorded as an adjustment"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 521140.0,
      "end_time": 524169.0,
      "text": "in the financial statements of the reporting period."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 524169.0,
      "end_time": 526720.0,
      "text": "This is very different than non-adjusting events"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 526720.0,
      "end_time": 529480.0,
      "text": "where the condition exists after the cut off date,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 529480.0,
      "end_time": 531190.0,
      "text": "after the reporting period, which"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 531190.0,
      "end_time": 533200.0,
      "text": "is why the financial statements are never"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 533200.0,
      "end_time": 535090.0,
      "text": "adjusted for measurement."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 535090.0,
      "end_time": 536920.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s check your understanding just"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 536920.0,
      "end_time": 538870.0,
      "text": "to be sure you got the idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 538870.0,
      "end_time": 541120.0,
      "text": "Remember to pause the video and answer the question"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 541120.0,
      "end_time": 543630.0,
      "text": "before I do it for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 543630.0,
      "end_time": 546390.0,
      "text": "Your company purchased a property in downtown Toronto"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 546390.0,
      "end_time": 548580.0,
      "text": "for $1.2 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 548580.0,
      "end_time": 550620.0,
      "text": "The property used to be a gas station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 550620.0,
      "end_time": 552420.0,
      "text": "and your company plans to develop it"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 552420.0,
      "end_time": 554100.0,
      "text": "as a rental property."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 554100.0,
      "end_time": 555720.0,
      "text": "During the subsequent event period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 555720.0,
      "end_time": 558870.0,
      "text": "you discover that the soil on the property is contaminated"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 558870.0,
      "end_time": 562080.0,
      "text": "and the value of the land is severely impaired."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 562080.0,
      "end_time": 564360.0,
      "text": "Is this a subsequent event that requires"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 564360.0,
      "end_time": 567435.0,
      "text": "an adjustment or a non-adjusting subsequent event?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 573990.0,
      "end_time": 577110.0,
      "text": "The answer is A, an adjusting event."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 577110.0,
      "end_time": 579660.0,
      "text": "The land should be written down because the contamination"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 579660.0,
      "end_time": 582780.0,
      "text": "existed before the cut off date, and it materially"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 582780.0,
      "end_time": 585360.0,
      "text": "affects the measurement of the land value."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 585360.0,
      "end_time": 588390.0,
      "text": "The land should be written down, and the new lower value"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 588390.0,
      "end_time": 591660.0,
      "text": "would be reported on the year-end financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 591660.0,
      "end_time": 593820.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s it for subsequent events."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 593820.0,
      "end_time": 596140.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much for watching my video."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 596140.0,
      "end_time": 599000.0,
      "text": "I hope you found it helpful for your learning."
    }
  ]
}